---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
 title="Terms of Use | Stimmie's Guides"
 description="Terms for using Stimmie's Guides student resources."
>
 <main class="legal-page">
 <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; All guides</a>

 <header class="legal-header">
 <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
 <p class="legal-lede">
 Last updated: July 4, 2026. By using Stimmie's Guides you agree to these terms.
 </p>
 </header>

 <article class="legal-body">
 <section>
 <h2>About the site</h2>
 <p>
 Stimmie's Guides is a personal project by Stimmie. Content is provided for
 students as a convenience. It is <strong>not</strong> affiliated with, endorsed by,
 or maintained by UPLB or any official university office.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Accuracy and updates</h2>
 <p>
 Guides may be incomplete, outdated, or wrong. Policies, dates, and campus processes
 change. Verify important decisions with official university sources.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
 <ul>
 <li>Use the site lawfully and respectfully.</li>
 <li>Do not attempt to disrupt hosting, scrape aggressively, or probe for vulnerabilities.</li>
 <li>Do not misrepresent the site as an official UPLB publication.</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
 <p>
 Site text and layout are owned by Stimmie unless otherwise noted. You may share
 links freely. Do not republish large portions as if they were official university
 materials.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
 <p>
 The site is provided "as is" without warranties. Stimmie is not liable for
 decisions you make based on guide content.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Changes</h2>
 <p>
 These terms may be updated. Continued use after changes are posted constitutes
 acceptance of the revised terms.
 </p>
 </section>
 </article>
 </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.legal-page {
 max-width: 42rem;
 margin: 0 auto;
 padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
 }

.back-link {
 font-size: 0.8rem;
 color: #6b7280;
 text-decoration: none;
 }

.back-link:hover {
 color: #111;
 text-decoration: underline;
 }

.legal-header {
 margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
 }

.legal-header h1 {
 font-size: 1.75rem;
 margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
 }

.legal-lede {
 color: #4b5563;
 line-height: 1.6;
 margin: 0;
 }

.legal-body section {
 margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
 }

.legal-body h2 {
 font-size: 1.1rem;
 margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
 }

.legal-body p,
.legal-body li {
 color: #4b5563;
 line-height: 1.65;
 font-size: 0.95rem;
 }

.legal-body ul {
 margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
 padding-left: 1.25rem;
 }
</style>
